this folder contains the scripts necessary to install on the host machine that
is running freebsd as its main os

this contains bash scrips, temp folders, init scripts and more.

structure:

FBSD 
     |-src 
     |     |-bash---------------#actual workhorse scripts
     |     |-caddy--------------#caddyfile and others to ensure port forwarding
     |     |-install------------#self-building installation scripts
     |-lib 
     |     |-init_scripts-------#different os systems need different injection scripts
     |     |-cloud_images-------#temp storage for .iso files trasferred from shepherd
     |     |-backups------------#to backup dbs
     |-docs
    
last updated: 09/01/26